<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Beacon vs Claude — Five Capability Gaps</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0E2841;
    --navy-deep: #0A1E32;
    --blue: #156082;
    --blue-bright: #378ADD;
    --sky: #0F9ED5;
    --orange: #E97132;
    --orange-soft: #F5A66E;
    --paper: #FDFCF8;
    --paper-warm: #F7F3EB;
    --ink: #1A1A1A;
    --ink-soft: #3D4A57;
    --muted: #8A96A3;
    --border: #E4DFD4;
    --accent-red: #C8341F;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.5;
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* === Texture overlay === */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(233, 113, 50, 0.02) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(14, 40, 65, 0.02) 0%, transparent 40%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1080px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 48px 96px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* === HEADER === */
  .masthead {
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--navy);
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 24px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.1s forwards;
  }

  .masthead-left .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .masthead h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 52px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  .masthead h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .masthead-right {
    text-align: right;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .masthead-right .date {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* === Subheader + Controls === */
  .subheader {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.25s forwards;
  }

  .subheader p {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .controls {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .toggle-btn {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--navy);
    color: var(--navy);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .toggle-btn:hover {
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  .toggle-btn.active {
    background: var(--orange);
    border-color: var(--orange);
    color: white;
  }

  /* === CAPABILITY ROWS === */
  .rows {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .row {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--paper);
    position: relative;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .row.visible {
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease forwards;
  }

  .row:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(14, 40, 65, 0.08);
  }

  .row-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr auto auto;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    gap: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .row.expanded .row-header {
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
    background: var(--paper-warm);
  }

  .row-number {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--orange);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .row-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--navy);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .score {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .score.max { background: var(--orange); color: white; }
  .score.high { background: var(--blue); color: white; }

  .expand-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .row.expanded .expand-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  /* === ROW CONTENT === */
  .row-content {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.5s ease;
  }

  .row.expanded .row-content {
    max-height: 800px;
  }

  .row-inner {
    padding: 32px 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .panel {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .panel-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .panel.claude .panel-label {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .panel.beacon .panel-label {
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .visual-box {
    background: var(--paper-warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    height: 220px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .panel.beacon .visual-box {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-color: var(--navy);
  }

  .caption {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .panel.beacon .caption {
    color: var(--orange-soft);
  }

  .row-footer {
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .row-footer strong {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* === SIDE-BY-SIDE VIEW (Toggle mode) === */
  body.compare-mode .rows {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  body.compare-mode .row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  body.compare-mode .row-content {
    max-height: none;
  }

  body.compare-mode .row-inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  body.compare-mode .expand-icon {
    display: none;
  }

  body.compare-mode .row-header {
    cursor: default;
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
    background: var(--paper-warm);
  }

  body.compare-mode .row-number {
    font-size: 28px;
  }

  body.compare-mode .row-title {
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  /* === FOOTER === */
  .footer {
    margin-top: 80px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--navy);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 24px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 1.5s forwards;
  }

  .footer blockquote {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--navy);
    max-width: 720px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .footer blockquote em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--orange);
  }

  .footer-meta {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* === ANIMATIONS === */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes drawLine {
    from { stroke-dashoffset: 400; }
    to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; }
  }

  @keyframes drawEdge {
    from { stroke-dashoffset: 200; opacity: 0; }
    to { stroke-dashoffset: 0; opacity: 0.85; }
  }

  @keyframes popIn {
    0% { transform: scale(0); opacity: 0; }
    70% { transform: scale(1.15); opacity: 1; }
    100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
    50% { transform: scale(1.08); }
  }

  .row.expanded .network-edge {
    stroke-dasharray: 200;
    animation: drawEdge 0.8s ease forwards;
  }

  .row.expanded .network-node {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: popIn 0.4s ease forwards;
  }

  .row.expanded .hub-pulse {
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    transform-origin: center;
    transform-box: fill-box;
  }

  .row.expanded .trend-line {
    stroke-dasharray: 400;
    animation: drawLine 1.2s ease 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .row.expanded .trend-dot {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: popIn 0.3s ease forwards;
  }

  .row.expanded .bar-fill {
    transform-origin: left;
    animation: expandBar 0.8s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes expandBar {
    from { transform: scaleX(0); }
    to { transform: scaleX(1); }
  }

  .row.expanded .ladder-step {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: slideInLadder 0.4s ease forwards;
  }

  @keyframes slideInLadder {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .row.expanded .primitive-card {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: popIn 0.35s ease forwards;
  }

  /* === RESPONSIVE === */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container { padding: 32px 20px 64px; }
    .masthead { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .masthead h1 { font-size: 36px; }
    .masthead-right { text-align: left; }
    .subheader { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .subheader p { font-size: 16px; }
    .row-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .row-title { font-size: 18px; }
    .footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer blockquote { font-size: 20px; }
    .footer-meta { text-align: left; }
    body.compare-mode .rows { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* === PRINT STYLES === */
  @media print {
    @page {
      size: letter landscape;
      margin: 0.4in;
    }

    body {
      background: white;
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    body::before { display: none; }

    .container {
      max-width: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .controls { display: none; }

    .masthead { margin-bottom: 16px; padding-bottom: 12px; animation: none; opacity: 1; }
    .masthead h1 { font-size: 28px; }
    .subheader { margin-bottom: 16px; animation: none; opacity: 1; }
    .subheader p { font-size: 13px; }

    .rows {
      display: grid !important;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .row {
      break-inside: avoid;
      opacity: 1 !important;
      transform: none !important;
      animation: none !important;
    }

    .row-header {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      cursor: default;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border) !important;
      grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr auto;
    }

    .row-number { font-size: 22px; }
    .row-title { font-size: 13px; }
    .score { font-size: 9px; padding: 3px 7px; }
    .expand-icon { display: none; }

    .row-content { max-height: none !important; overflow: visible !important; }
    .row-inner {
      padding: 12px;
      gap: 8px;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .visual-box { height: 100px; }
    .panel-label { font-size: 8px; padding-bottom: 4px; }
    .caption { font-size: 8px; }

    .row-footer {
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      animation: none;
      opacity: 1;
    }
    .footer blockquote { font-size: 14px; }

    .row.expanded .network-edge,
    .row.expanded .network-node,
    .row.expanded .hub-pulse,
    .row.expanded .trend-line,
    .row.expanded .trend-dot,
    .row.expanded .bar-fill,
    .row.expanded .ladder-step,
    .row.expanded .primitive-card {
      animation: none !important;
      opacity: 1 !important;
      stroke-dasharray: none !important;
      stroke-dashoffset: 0 !important;
      transform: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

  <header class="masthead">
    <div class="masthead-left">
      <div class="eyebrow">Capability Assessment · Internal</div>
      <h1>Beacon <em>vs</em> Claude</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="masthead-right">
      <div class="date">April 2026</div>
      <div>Vine &amp; Fig Tree</div>
      <div>Partner Success</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="subheader">
    <p>Five capability gaps where Beacon structurally outperforms a generalist reasoning layer — ranked by demo impact.</p>
    <div class="controls">
      <button class="toggle-btn active" id="view-default" onclick="setView('default')">Expanded</button>
      <button class="toggle-btn" id="view-compare" onclick="setView('compare')">Side by side</button>
      <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="window.print()">Print · PDF</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rows" id="rows">

    <!-- ROW 1: FMI Network -->
    <article class="row expanded" data-row="1">
      <div class="row-header" onclick="toggleRow(1)">
        <div class="row-number">01</div>
        <div class="row-title">FMI network mapping</div>
        <div class="score max">5 / 5</div>
        <svg class="expand-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><line x1="10" y1="4" x2="10" y2="16"/><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="16" y2="10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="row-content">
        <div class="row-inner">
          <div class="panel claude">
            <div class="panel-label">Claude</div>
            <div class="visual-box">
              <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 260 220">
                <circle cx="55" cy="68" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="95" cy="100" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="165" cy="75" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="205" cy="115" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="75" cy="140" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="145" cy="145" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="225" cy="155" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="50" cy="180" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
                <circle cx="180" cy="190" r="4" fill="#8A96A3"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="caption">Isolated results · No relations</div>
          </div>
          <div class="panel beacon">
            <div class="panel-label">Beacon</div>
            <div class="visual-box">
              <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 260 220">
                <g stroke="#378ADD" stroke-width="1.2" opacity="0.85" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round">
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.1s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="78" y2="60"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.15s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="130" y2="40"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.2s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="182" y2="60"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.25s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="215" y2="92"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.3s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="225" y2="135"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.35s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="195" y2="175"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.4s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="130" y2="195"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.45s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="65" y2="175"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.5s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="35" y2="135"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.55s" x1="130" y1="112" x2="45" y2="92"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.7s" x1="78" y1="60" x2="130" y2="40"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.75s" x1="130" y1="40" x2="182" y2="60"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.8s" x1="182" y1="60" x2="215" y2="92"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.85s" x1="215" y1="92" x2="225" y2="135"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.9s" x1="225" y1="135" x2="195" y2="175"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:0.95s" x1="195" y1="175" x2="130" y2="195"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1s" x1="130" y1="195" x2="65" y2="175"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.05s" x1="65" y1="175" x2="35" y2="135"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.1s" x1="35" y1="135" x2="45" y2="92"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.15s" x1="45" y1="92" x2="78" y2="60"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.25s" x1="78" y1="60" x2="182" y2="60"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.3s" x1="45" y1="92" x2="215" y2="92"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.35s" x1="35" y1="135" x2="225" y2="135"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.4s" x1="65" y1="175" x2="195" y2="175"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.45s" x1="130" y1="40" x2="65" y2="175"/>
                  <line class="network-edge" style="animation-delay:1.5s" x1="130" y1="40" x2="195" y2="175"/>
                </g>
                <g fill="#378ADD">
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.3s" cx="78" cy="60" r="5"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.35s" cx="130" cy="40" r="4"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.4s" cx="182" cy="60" r="5.5"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.45s" cx="215" cy="92" r="4"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.5s" cx="225" cy="135" r="5"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.55s" cx="195" cy="175" r="4"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.6s" cx="130" cy="195" r="4.5"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.65s" cx="65" cy="175" r="4"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.7s" cx="35" cy="135" r="5"/>
                  <circle class="network-node" style="animation-delay:0.75s" cx="45" cy="92" r="4.5"/>
                </g>
                <circle class="hub-pulse" cx="130" cy="112" r="12" fill="#E97132"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="caption">Curated actors · Weighted edges · Follower reach</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row-footer">
          <strong>Why it matters:</strong> a curated actor registry with follower-weighted reach lets you map who moved a narrative first and who amplified it — with network edges, not just a list.
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- ROW 2: Citation Architecture -->
    <article class="row" data-row="2">
      <div class="row-header" onclick="toggleRow(2)">
        <div class="row-number">02</div>
        <div class="row-title">Structural citation architecture</div>
        <div class="score max">5 / 5</div>
        <svg class="expand-icon" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><line x1="10" y1="4" x2="10" y2="16"/><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="16" y2="10"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="row-content">
        <div class="row-inner">
          <div class="panel claude">
            <div class="panel-label">Claude</div>
            <div class="visual-box">
              <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 260 220">
                <rect x="30" y="60" width="200" height="24" rx="3" fill="#E4DFD4"/>
